and cheese in the Bay Area,

00:28:23.140 --> 00:28:24.920
but it's not the same.

00:28:24.920 --> 00:28:28.800
Just eat a lot of cheese,
because it's spectacular.

00:28:28.800 --> 00:28:31.340
