00:45:39.460 --> 00:45:41.930
And I see stuff, and I
can't help but buying it,

00:45:41.930 --> 00:45:44.400
and I buy too much of
it, and I make sorbet.

00:45:44.400 --> 00:45:45.930
And I always make fruit with it.

00:45:45.930 --> 00:45:48.320
I love cookies, I'm
always making cookies.

00:45:48.320 --> 00:45:50.120
I make a lot of biscotti.

00:45:50.120 --> 00:45:51.950
I would do sable,
the French cookies,

00:45:51.950 --> 00:45:53.640
the thin ones with the butter.

00:45:53.640 --> 00:45:55.580
With lime zest, or something.

00:45:55.580 --> 00:45:58.900
So I make a lot of those
kind of things for dessert.

00:45:58.900 --> 00:46:02.240
