or something, I work at home.

00:46:02.240 --> 00:46:04.150
I'm always slicing pieces off.

00:46:04.150 --> 00:46:05.990
And I'll just scrape
some of the icing.

00:46:05.990 --> 00:46:08.500
Oh I can't eat, that
piece doesn't have icing,

00:46:08.500 --> 00:46:10.830
let me cut it.

00:46:10.830 --> 00:46:12.330
I have neighbors,
and they're always

00:46:12.330 --> 00:46:15.630
