two slices out.

00:46:15.630 --> 00:46:17.130
JONATHAN ALFERNESS:
This one's left.

00:46:17.130 --> 00:46:18.005
DAVID LEBOVITZ: Yeah.

00:46:18.005 --> 00:46:20.544
Like, thanks, I think.

